<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>马当路练习生｜AI职场人格测评2.0</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --red: #FF4D6D;
            --red-light: #FF7F96;
            --red-pale: #FFF0F3;
            --red-mid: #FFD6DD;
            --dark: #1A1A1A;
            --gray: #6B7280;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --cream: #FFFAF8;
            --gold: #F59E0B;
            --green: #10B981;
            --shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255,77,109,0.15);
            --shadow-lg: 0 20px 60px rgba(255,77,109,0.2);
        }
        *{margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;}
        body{background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF0F3 0%, #FFE5EC 100%); min-height: 100vh; padding: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;}
        .container{width: 100%; max-width: 440px; background: var(--white); border-radius: 24px; padding: 32px 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8); position: relative; overflow: hidden;}
        .container::before {content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 6px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--red-light));}
        .title{text-align: center; color: var(--dark); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;}
        .title span {color: var(--red);}
        .desc{text-align: center; color: var(--gray); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; font-weight: 500;}
        .option-box{display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;}
        .option{border: 2px solid #F3F4F6; background: var(--cream); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); position: relative;}
        .option:hover{border-color: var(--red-light); background: var(--red-pale); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
        .option h3{color: var(--dark); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 6px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;}
        .option p{color: var(--gray); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400;}
        
        /* 答题卡样式 */
        .quiz-box {display: none;}
        .quiz-progress {height: 6px; background: #E5E7EB; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 24px; overflow: hidden;}
        .quiz-progress-bar {height: 100%; width: 33%; background: var(--red); transition: width 0.3s ease;}
        .quiz-question {font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.4;}
        .quiz-options {display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;}
        .quiz-opt-btn {padding: 16px; border: 2px solid #E5E7EB; background: var(--white); border-radius: 12px; text-align: left; font-size: 14px; color: var(--dark); font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;}
        .quiz-opt-btn:hover {border-color: var(--red); background: var(--red-pale); color: var(--red); font-weight: 600;}

        /* 授权弹窗 */
        .pop-box{display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.6); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 1000; padding: 20px;}
        .pop-content{width: 100%; max-width: 360px; background: var(--white); border-radius: 24px; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); animation: popScale 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);}
        @keyframes popScale { from { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0; } to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; } }
        .pop-icon {width: 56px; height: 56px; background: var(--red-pale); color: var(--red); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 auto 16px;}
        .pop-content h3{color: var(--dark); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px;}
        .pop-sub {font-size: 13px; color: #9CA3AF; margin-top: 12px; line-height: 1.4;}
        .pop-btn{margin-top: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;}
        .btn{padding: 14px 24px; border-radius: 14px; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; width: 100%; transition: all 0.2s;}
        .btn-yes{background: var(--red); color: var(--white); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,77,109,0.3);}
        .btn-yes:hover {background: #E03A58;}
        .btn-no{background: #F3F4F6; color: var(--gray);}
        .btn-no:hover {background: #E5E7EB;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div id="homePhase">
            <h2 class="title">马当路练习生 <span>AI测评2.0</span></h2>
            <p class="desc">结合小红书AI Native创新项目，测你的专属职场赛道</p>
            <div class="option-box">
                <div class="option" id="shortTest">
                    <h3>⚡ 1分钟轻量AI潜力探测</h3>
                    <p>快速洞察你在小红书REDébuilt生态中的内容网感与原生AI直觉。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="option" id="longTest">
                    <h3>✨ 深度专业级大厂通关测评</h3>
                    <p>全面解析多维能力，定向匹配垂类内容运营赛道，输出面试核心策略。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="quizPhase" class="quiz-box">
            <div class="quiz-progress"><div class="quiz-progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div></div>
            <div class="quiz-question" id="questionText">问题加载中...</div>
            <div class="quiz-options" id="optionsBox"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pop-box" id="authPop">
        <div class="pop-content">
            <div class="pop-icon">✨</div>
            <h3>AI 评估报告已生成！</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">检测到您是<b>成均馆大学商科</b>背景，拥有知名大厂及新媒体矩阵丰富运营经验，契合度达 <b>98.5%</b>！</p>
            <div class="pop-btn">
                <button class="btn btn-yes" id="agreeBtn">授权数据并一键内推</button>
                <button class="btn btn-no" id="refuseBtn">仅查看我的职场人格海报</button>
            </div>
            <p class="pop-sub">💡 授权后，本次AI测评表现将直接同步至小红书校招系统，优先获得马当路练习生面试机会。</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const shortTest = document.getElementById('shortTest');
        const longTest = document.getElementById('longTest');
        const homePhase = document.getElementById('homePhase');
        const quizPhase = document.getElementById('quizPhase');
        const questionText = document.getElementById('questionText');
        const optionsBox = document.getElementById('optionsBox');
        const progressBar = document.getElementById('progressBar');
        const authPop = document.getElementById('authPop');
        const agreeBtn = document.getElementById('agreeBtn');
        const refuseBtn = document.getElementById('refuseBtn');

        let currentQuestion = 0;
        const questions = [
            {
                q: "1. 面对小红书2.0版本中新增的『AI native创新项目』，你更倾向于如何产出业务解法？",
                opts: [
                    "A. 纯靠直觉或传统经验，走一步看一步",
                    "B. 结合大语言模型分析小红书垂类大盘数据，用AI高效辅助策略生成",
                    "C. 独立用低代码/H5全链路跑通Demo，用真实上线作品向Owner说话"
                ]
            },
            {
                q: "2. 在进行成均馆大学新媒体矩阵从0到1的冷启动时，如果遇到流量瓶颈，你首选的突破口是？",
                opts: [
                    "A. 维持原样，等待平台自然推荐",
                    "B. 联动头部校园KOL打造爆款大促/创意综艺，实现跨界引流破圈",
                    "C. 精细化拆解目标受众画像，进行精细化社群裂变与爆款内容复刻"
                ]
            },
            {
                q: "3. 假如你作为内容运营练习生，负责一个全新的垂类赛道，你认为核心的Builder精神是？",
                opts: [
                    "A. 做好被分配的基础执行工作即可",
                    "B. 跨部门整合资源，主动开拓校企对接，不依赖现有资源解决问题",
                    "C. 独立闭环，不仅能写文案，还能懂用户思维、懂技术落地，全栈输出"
                ]
            }
        ];

        function startQuiz() {
            homePhase.style.display = 'none';
            quizPhase.style.display = 'block';
            showQuestion();
        }

        function showQuestion() {
            progressBar.style.width = ((currentQuestion + 1) / questions.length) * 100 + '%';
            questionText.innerText = questions[currentQuestion].q;
            optionsBox.innerHTML = '';
            questions[currentQuestion].opts.forEach(opt => {
                const btn = document.createElement('button');
                btn.className = 'quiz-opt-btn';
                btn.innerText = opt;
                btn.onclick = () => nextStep();
                optionsBox.appendChild(btn);
            });
        }

        function nextStep() {
            currentQuestion++;
            if (currentQuestion < questions.length) {
                showQuestion();
            } else {
                quizPhase.style.display = 'none';
                authPop.style.display = 'flex';
            }
        }

        shortTest.onclick = startQuiz;
        longTest.onclick = startQuiz;

        agreeBtn.onclick = ()=>{
            alert('🎉 授权成功！已为你匹配专属绿色通道，即将跳转简历一键投递页面。高同学，马当路见！');
            authPop.style.display = 'none';
            window.location.href = "https://job.xiaohongshu.com/";
        }

        refuseBtn.onclick = ()=>{
            alert('已为你生成专属职场人格海报！感谢参与，欢迎分享种草！');
            authPop.style.display = 'none';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
